description:
Operators of warehouse-style, no frills stores that sell a wide variety
of merchandise in bulk, and concentrate on price appeal. Such
merchants may or may not have membership requirements.
Products for sale may include household supplies and appliances,
office supplies and equipment, dry groceries and perishables,
household and office furniture, electronics, and auto supplies.
